result.name: My Last 3 Days
result.short_summary: Some would die to be famous. Others are killed.
result.full_summary: Josie King is murdered after a video of her singing goes viral. Relive the last 3 days of her life through her phone and discover who killed her – and why...

data.content: Are you ok??
Of course, why do you ask?
You just seemed a little weird last night
Weird how?
Quiet. Not yourself. Like something's bothering you.
Is everything ok with you and dad?
Everything is fine lovely. Don't you worry xxx
If you say so xxx
Hey it was nice to meet you!!
You too Josie! Always nice to meet sane people on holiday. Usually it's just wierdos lol.
I know what you mean lol
Back to rainy Manchester now though. Bit of a change from 30 degree heat..
Never been to Manchester. Can't be that bad though right?
No, it's lovely, but I was thinking about maybe moving to London for a change, but don't think I'm going to go really
Why not?
That would be incredible
I dunno
Gut feeling. Something's holding me back...
Hmm. Normally I'd say trust you gut, but sometimes, it's good to ignore it.
Where would you live though?
Suppose it's expensive in London isn't it.
Yeah it is.
Although I've got a couple of friends down there who I used to live with at uni who are trying to get me to move in with them.
No way!!!
Well surely that's a done deal then?
What do you mean?
Well it's fate.
You need a change
You want a new challenge
And your friends are down there already...
I know we only met for a bit on holiday, but I REALLY think you should go.
Besides, I'm planning on moving to London maybe for uni. If I'm down there, we should totally meet up.
Hello. My friend Kam gave me your number as he said that you run a recording studio? I was wondering if you could give me some idea of prices. Thanks, Josie
Hahaha
I dunno, do you really think I should?
Well obviously I won't force you, but if I were you, I'd jump at the chance.
It will be an amazing life experience.
You know what, I think you're slowly convincing me...
Good!!!
What's the worst that could happen?
Ok something's not right.
I heard you crying last night mum
What aren't you telling me?
I don't like that you're keeping things from me when I know something's not ok.
You know you can tell me anything don't you?!
I do. I'm sorry.
Listen, it's nothing to worry about ok
I just found a lump the other week and the doctor has referred me to see a consultant
So just got a bit upset about that, but your dad is being really supportive.
OMG Mum why didn't you tell me straight away?
We didn't want you to worry, and if everyone is worrying for me, I'll worry more about it
Well of course I'm going to worry about you! You're my mum!
When's your appointment with the consultant?
A week away, the doctor was keen to get me infront of someone pretty quickly.
How come? What do you think that means?
I don't know, I'm sure it's just a precaution, you know what they're like with these things!
Well OK, let's chat more later tonight when you're back from work OK?
Of course 🙂 and please don't worry.
I'm sure it's nothing xxx
Hey Josie, sorry for the late reply. Sure thing. It's only a small recording studio I've set up myself, but the sound quality is perfect.
In terms of prices: I normally charge £60 per hour, but being as you're a mate of Kam's I can do it for half price @ £30. How does that sound?
If you want to go ahead, just HMU and let me know when, and how long you think you'll need and I can book it in.

Hey mum, just wanted to say I hated seeing you upset last night. I feel almost responsible because I made you talk about it. But I think it's best I know so I can help you through it. I'm also here for you if you ever need to chat or need someone to accompany you to the doctors. Like I said, I'm sure it's nothing to worry about, but whatever happens, we'll get through it as a family 🙂 xxx
Thanks Josie, I know you are 🙂 xXx
Aw awesome. Yes that would be amazing. How about next Monday for 3 hours?
Can you do evenings? I'll be coming from work and don't finish until 5 so maybe 6-9 would be ideal?
Sure.
That's no problem.
See you next Monday @ 6!
Perfect, thanks 🙂 x
Yo Josie, just wanna say you're a rare talent! Your voice is strong and love your songs. Lemme know when you wanna go again and we can do some more.
Thanks Jimmy, I've been meaning to record some stuff for a while, just haven't had the confidence to be honest!
Well you should!
I see a lot of artists in here, a lot of wannabes too. Most don't have a chance in hell, but you're good!
I know some great musicians though too. Let me know if you want me to link you up with any of them.
Could be a few interesting collabs I can make happen.
Haha, maybe, let's see! I'm just doing this as hobbie to be honest, nothing serious ya know!
No worries, well let me know either way, no pressure!
Hey Jessica
Really nice to meet you at the studio the other day
Be great to keep chatting!
Hy hy Josie!!
Gr8 to meet u 2!
And for sure.
Us singers need to stick 2geva
It's hard out there
Is it?
4 sure
U think ur climbing to the top
Then sum1 knocks u down
Has that happened to you?
Ye
Many times
Spoken 2 a few labels, but they didn't think I was good enuff which is total 💩
But ur wasting ur time. It's so hard 2 break into this industry
How come?
It's all bout who u no
If u don't no the boss or his son, then ur screwed
I can imagine
It scares me how hard it all is, that's why I went to uni really. Just doing this singing as a hobbie really!
Ye, ur best doing that
I've been trying 4 yrs
So close 2 givin up
Don't give up! You're really good 😊
I'll keep singing
But trust me, I'm at the point where trying 2 break in2 the industry is so demoralising
It's way 2 competitive
People like us don't have a chance lol
Trust me
Fingers crossed it works out for one of us then!
It won't.
I promise u.
Good luck today Mum! Let me know how it goes and what the consultant says as soon as you're out please!
Will do, thanks Josie xXx
What did he say??
Mum?
Outgoing call: not answered
Outgoing call: not answered
Please call me when you get this and let me know how it went xxxx
Call from Mum: duration 20:54
Just wanted to say again Mum, I'm sure you can get beat this, and me and dad are going to be here to help you get through it 100%. I love you xxxxxx
Thanks Josie, looking forward to seeing you when you get home xXx
I can't believe the news about Mum, is she ok?
Devastated Josie if I'm honest.
We both are
She really needs us right now
I'll be home as soon as I can xxxx
Are you ok today? Hated seeing you so upset last night xxx
I'm ok Dad, just a shock hearing your mum has cancer
Is there literally nothing they can do??
Well chemo is obviously an option, but they need to do some more tests to see if it has spread first
And when will they be?
Next couple of weeks. I'm trying to fast-track it on the insurance, but you know what it's like.
I'm sure everything will be fine, we all just need to try and stay positive and support your mum through this.
Of course xxx
Yo Josie.
Heard you've been speaking to Jessica lol
Ha, yes.
You're response says it all!
Lovely girl, but negative as a double-ended battery.
Hahaha, I know what you mean
Yeah, don't take what she says too seriously. If you did, you'd never do anything in life lol
Noted.
What time is mum's scan today?
4pm
OK will text her good luck xxx
Good luck with the second scan today Mum, thinking of you xxxx
Thanks, hope it goes ok, feeling nervous xXx
My fingers are crossed for you 🤞
All done, get the results in the next week. They just need a specialist to look at all the evidence. Feeling pretty upbeat though xXx
Good, you need to, and you know we're all here for you anyway, whatever happens! xxx
I know. I'm so lucky to have you and your dad. Couldn't ask for a more beautiful family!
Is Zach coming over tonight? I was thinking of cooking some pasta and some garlic bread if you two fancy it? Let me know as I'm going to the shops in a bit xXx
We are yes. And that sounds delicious. I hope it's Spag bol? You know that's my favourite...
Yes 🙂 I can't believe you don't know how to cook it, it's pretty simple Josie lol xXx
Why would I need to when you cook it all the time??
Very true! One day you will xXx
Hope the results are ok mum, please let me know what they say xxx
Thanks Josie xXx will do.
Missed call
Can you ring me please?
Just at work, can ring in about an hour, everything ok?
Not really. Your mum has her results, not good news x
Outgoing call: duration 20:22
How are you doing today Mum?
Still pretty low, but it's too be expected I suppose
You need to stay positive though, we all do.
I know, I just know there's nothing they can really do. It's stage 4 cancer. Not many people recover from that, it's near impossible when it spreads to your bones.
Not like they can give me a new skeleton is it
No but they can try and control it
Let's hope so xXx

No need to panic, but your mum collapsed today, on the way to the hospital with her now. She's ok, but bit shaken. I think they're going to keep her in overnight to make sure she's ok. Maybe give her a text?

So it's not good news. They want to keep her in for assesment. They're worried she's getting progressively worse too soon, probably because of the chemo
Did they say anymore on the diagnosis? Do they still thing she only has 6 months to live??

Well that's their estimate. Once it has spread to the bones there's not much they can do. The doctor said it's just about seeing that she's as comfortable as possible now and trying to prolongue her life as long as possible
I can't even believe this has happened
I'm literally in tears
So am I Josie, it's not going to be easy any of this. I really thought I'd lost her yesterday when she collapsed
Can't believe I'm going to say this
But I thought she'd gone
Oh dad, it must have been awful
The good thing is she hasn't, she's still here and we just need to hope she's with us for a long time yet
We both just need to stay strong for your mum
I know xxx
You deleted this conversation.
How are you feeling mum? I'm going to come and visit you around 7pm tonight, that ok?
Yes, would like that. See you then xXx
Josie please let's chat about all this
Screw you Zach
You fucked someone else
Cheaters don't get second chances with me
No Jos
Honestly
Please
Let me explain

Josie you're overreacting

Missed call
Please pick up the phone
Missed call
Josie

Don't make me beg
Missed call

Zach

Stop

You are NEVER getting another chance with me. I am not a girl who gives second chances. You break my trust, you break EVERYTHING. We've been together for 3 years for fuck sake. We've talked about everything. The future, buying a house, marriage, kids. And then you go to one party and bang some girl, for what? You've lost me Zach. Nothing you do will ever get me back. I am worth WAY more than that. I don't do deserve to be treated like this, I deserve someone who's honest, and only has eyes for me. And the sad thing is, I thought that person was you. I will be civil to you, I will acknowledge you, fuck I'll probably still love you, but I will NEVER let you back into my life. And the only person you have to blame is yourself.
Missed call

Josie. Shit. I don't even know how to say this. I'm sorry, ok? From the bottom of my heart, I truly am. I don't know what came over me, it's not the kind of the person I am, or pride myself on being. We had 3 amazing years together and I don't want to throw it all away just because of one silly mistake. And that's exactly what it was. A mistake! I don't fancy that girl one bit. She was, and is nothing to me. I just got drunk and I wasn't thinking straight. You know I wouldn't do this on purpose, I'm literally begging you to take me back Jos, I can't imagine life without you.

Don't you dare try and make excuses. Alcohol doesn't MAKE you do anything. You're in control of how much you drink, and you are still in control of your decisions whether you're drunk or your sober. And besides, you slept with her!!! Every piece of clothing you took off her was a decision. You could have stopped at any point. If you were that sorry, you'd have told me straight away, but you didn't, I found out through one of my friends. Do you have any idea of how embarassing that is for me? That I was totally unaware you'd cheated for a good two weeks afterwards? I even slept with you ffs. I have never felt so used, dirty and ashamed to be with you and nothing you say can make up for what you did. And if you think I'm one of those girls who gives in, then think again. I'm worth so much more than that.
I don't know what to say...
There is NOTHING you can say.
Just move on and get on with your life.

Your dad told me about Zach and what he did to you. I know I'm 30 years older than you and things are different now for your generation, but I'm here if you want to talk about anything, I'm sure I can try and give you some sort of advice, or if you want a shoulder to cry on, you can always come and visit me, you know that.

Neither did I. Just shows you what a sucker I really am. Can't believe I let someone do this to me and then hide it from me for weeks!
Seriously.
Fuck you.

Some boys are just very good at hiding things Josie, you can't blame yourself. You're such a beautiful and honest young woman. That's what I love about you most, and it kills me to know someone would want to hurt my daughter like he did.
❤️thanks mum, means a lot
Remember, heartache is like a bruise. The pain will heal with time.
Make sure you chat to your dad about it too. He always was a good listener, that's what made me fall in love with him. He always seemed like he cared about everything I told him.
You two are so lovey dovey it's sickening 🤢
Missed call

Hey Jimmy, long time no speak!
I've been writing some new songs recently, wondered if I could have some studio time to test them out.

I know it's a week and a half away but, things are pretty mad atm (tell you bout it when I see ya!)

Can we do an evening again?
Sure, 6-9?
Perfect! Thanks Jimmy.
NP

It's over.
Thanks for coming to see me last night, it was lovely seeing you

Remember you can always do better than a boy who cheats on you. You're worth so much more than that and you will eventually find someone who loves you so much that they won't ever contemplate looking at another girl.
I know mum, it's just so annoying, I really thought Zach was 'the one'. This is the second time a boy has cheated on me now, and I really thought Zach was different.
So did I, if I'm honest. You just need to have a bit of time to yourself and then find yourself a nice boy. Maybe there's someone you already know who might be perfect for you??? 😉
NO Mum

He's just a lovely boy isn't he. Tall, good looking and clearly cares about you. You'd be perfect for each other.
You make me 🤢he's like a brother you know that
I'm just clearly pointing out that you're well suited. And sometimes those closest to us are more perfect for us than we realise.
I'm not having this conversation mum, we've had it many times before lol
Hey Josie you on your way?
Sorry, had some bad news so can't make it, will explain tomorrow.

Hey Jimmy, really sorry about last night. My mum sadly passed away yesterday so as you can imagine I was all over the place. I'll still pay you though, let me know how much I owe you and I'll transfer you the money. Again, really sorry!
Shit Josie, so sorry to hear that, but don't worry, no harm done. And don't worry about paying, these things happen. Just look after yourself and HMU when you're ready. Take care x

Josie. Please pick up the phone. Please talk to me. I literally don't think I can go on without you in my life. I swear, I will never EVER do anything like that again. I swear on my mum's life!!!

I'm lying in bed and I can't sleep. I've been trying for hours, but my brain literally won't switch off. I normally hate it, but tonight I remembered the first night of uni. It was Fresher's night, our first taste of uni life. I was hiding in a corner like a deer in headlights, so outta my depth partying in a big city compared to the little town I came from, but then I saw you. I could tell this life was alien to you too, but you were so beautiful and as soon as you spoke to me, you put me at ease. You were wearing that light cream dress. We got talking and I joked that you better not spill any drinks down you, else you'd never get it out! You said that wearing a white dress was pretty forward considering we'd just met too. Then we exchanged numbers, then 3 dates later, we became official. Cheating on you was the biggest regret of my life because I was so blind to the fact that the most perfect girl was right in front of me the whole time. I will do anything to get you back. Don't think I'm going to stop xxxxxx
